Nana

381
00:21:08,728 --> 00:21:13,718
I reached into the sky

382
00:21:13,828 --> 00:21:20,238
But I couldn't reach what I wanted

383
00:21:20,438 --> 00:21:25,608
They grew smaller
and disappeared into the sky

384
00:21:25,608 --> 00:21:31,608
Like colorful balloons

385
00:21:31,788 --> 00:21:33,718
I'm alone

386
00:21:33,718 --> 00:21:37,448
My hand had no place to go

387
00:21:37,618 --> 00:21:44,088
And gently you took it

388
00:21:44,198 --> 00:21:45,268
Starless night

389
00:21:45,268 --> 00:21:49,458
I won't look back
at the shadow of my past

390
00:21:49,698 --> 00:21:55,268
I want to feel your warmth

391
00:21:55,878 --> 00:21:57,138
Tears are falling down

392
00:21:57,138 --> 00:22:01,238
Even if I'm unsure I won't let go

393
00:22:01,318 --> 00:22:07,738
Of your hand holding mine

